Class Frames

java.lang.Object
app.tracktune.utils.Frames
public class Frames extends Object
Utility class containing constants for frame dimensions and FXML view paths used throughout the application.

This class centralizes all frame-related constants such as widths, heights, and resource paths for easy maintenance and localization.
